any_downsizing_allowance.browser_title = Are you claiming any downsizing allowance?
any_downsizing_allowance.title = Are you claiming any downsizing allowance?
any_downsizing_allowance.guidance1 = In order to claim downsizing allowance:
any_downsizing_allowance.guidance1.bullet1 = the deceased must have disposed of a former home and either downsized to a less valuable home, or ceased to own a home, on or after 8 July 2015
any_downsizing_allowance.guidance1.bullet2 = the former home would have qualified for the RNRB if it had been kept until death
any_downsizing_allowance.guidance1.bullet3 = at least some of the estate is inherited by the deceased’s direct descendants
any_downsizing_allowance.guidance2 = The downsizing addition can’t exceed the maximum amount of RNRB that would have been available if the disposal or downsizing hadn’t happened.
